 <text>
  <front>
   <head>The DREAM.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">AH stay, fair fleeting Form, I charge thee stay;</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Whither, ah whither wouldst thou glide away?</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">calls thee, lovely cruel Shade!</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">bids thee stay, thy once lov'd Maid!</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Alas! in vain I call, for see he flies;</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Flies my fond clasping Arms, and ardent Eyes.</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Not all my Prayers can the lov'd Form detain:</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">My Sighs, my Tears, my Wishes are in vain.</l>
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">In gentle Slumbers,  close my Eyes,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And bid once more the lovely Phantom rise.</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Bid him in all those heavenly Charms appear;</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">That melting Softness, that engaging Air,</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">In that too powerful Sorrow let him shine,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">When first he gave his Heart and conquer'd mine.</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Hence then, ye Sorrows, from the fancied Scene,</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Despairs, eternal Sighs, and secret Pain,</l>
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Shall wound no more, no Thought my Bliss destroy;</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">No happy Rival interrupt my Joy:</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">For oh! whate'er my cruel Fates Design,</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">In Sleep  can be only mine.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
